‚Ä¢ Target Range: R${userData.targetSalary || 25000}+ per month
‚Ä¢ Negotiable based on benefits package`
                ];
                
                return templates.join('\n\n') + '\n\n' + cvText;
            }
            
            generateCoverLetter(userData) {
